{"tid":935521,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"我個chrome怪怪地","createTime":"2018-12-10T05:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T16:30:50.000Z","uid":158513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"24c16960c83737bed92944311119e2f6e9664c89","tid":935521,"uid":158513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:31:00.000Z","msg":"半年前砌左新腦<br />\n用chrome上網有時上到，有時load好耐上唔到<br />\n原因err_time_out，隔分零鐘f5又上到<br />\n其他要連線軟件冇問題，打機冇斷線，wifi冇問題，其他連router既設備都冇事<br />\n所以好肯定淨係關部腦事<br />\n<br />\n上網睇過教刪cookies打指令重裝chrome更新LAN Driver都試晒冇料到<br />\n最近發現chrome load好耐時只要一開IE或者firefox其他瀏覽器，load個網就會一下load完<br />\n用其他瀏覽器冇load好耐依個問題，load youtube片都係即刻睇到，反而chrome要轉菊花幾秒<br />\n有冇巴打遇過依種情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n補充多少少，入router睇流量，chrome 上唔到網時得幾KB/s流量，冇連線咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865a017e88d3412693c4c898dd33ba401dc47deb","tid":935521,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:32:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e4c3d6261447ca5f50a5d1eb1ccd1785bd5e24a","tid":935521,"uid":158513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T10:50:35.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2152bed1448630c0d2d61b8017d9b280ccfa39d8","tid":935521,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"865a017e88d3412693c4c898dd33ba401dc47deb","tid":935521,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:32:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T11:27:44.000Z","msg":"你出錢？"},{"pid":"d55549c9fc91746526683114456bcbffd5fe818a","tid":935521,"uid":497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T11:35:27.000Z","msg":"會唔會有啲chrome既插件卡住左"},{"pid":"5745deae6e937f9a5621ffa7ba20114d3ea68255","tid":935521,"uid":158513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d55549c9fc91746526683114456bcbffd5fe818a","tid":9